#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:23
msgid ""
"By default, the WAPT Server is configured with a single "
":term:`SuperAdmin` account whose password is setup during initial post-"
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"En version WAPT Community, le serveur WAPT est configuré pour utiliser un"
" compte :term:`SuperAdmin` unique dont le mot de passe est défini lors de"
" la post-configuration."

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:26
msgid ""
"On large and security-minded network, this :term:`SuperAdmin` account "
"should not be used since it cannot provide the necessary traceability for"
" administrative actions that are done on the network."
msgstr ""
"Ce compte :term:`SuperAdmin` ne doit pas être utilisé si une traçabilité "
"nominative des actions d'administration du parc est recherchée."

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:30
msgid ""
"It is thus necessary to configure authentication against the "
":term:`Organization`'s Active Directory for the :term:`Administrators` "
"and the :term:`Package Deployers`; this will allow to use named accounts "
"for administrative tasks."
msgstr ""
"Il est impératif de configurer l'authentification Active Directory de "
"l':term:`Organisation` qui permettra l'utilisation des identifiants "
"nominatifs des :term:`Administrateurs` et des :term:`Déployeurs de "
"Paquets`."

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:37
msgid ""
"Active Directory authentication is used to authenticate access to the "
"inventory via the WAPT Console;"
msgstr ""
"l'authentification Active Directory est utilisée pour donner des accès à "
"l'inventaire des postes à travers la console WAPT ;"

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:40
msgid ""
"however, all actions on the WAPT equipped remote devices are based on "
"X.509 signatures, so an :term:`Administrator` will need both an Active "
"Directory login **AND** a private key whose certificate is recognized by "
"the remote devices to manage his installed base of devices using WAPT;"
msgstr ""
"toutefois, toutes les actions sur les postes sont basées sur les "
"signature X.509, donc un :term:`Administrateur` aura besoin à la fois "
"d'un login Active Directory **ET** d'une clef privée reconnue par les "
"postes équipés de WAPT pour effectuer des tâches d'administration du parc"
" avec WAPT ;"

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:46
msgid ""
"only the :term:`SuperAdmin` account and the members of the Active "
"Directory security group **waptadmins** will be allowed to upload "
"packages on the main repository (authentication mode by login and "
"password);"
msgstr ""
"seuls le compte :term:`SuperAdmin` et les membres du groupe de sécurité "
"Active Directory **waptadmins** pourront charger des paquets sur le dépôt"
" WAPT (mode d'authentification par login / mot de passe) ;"

