#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:77
msgid ""
"Enabling SSL/ TLS support for the LDAP connection to the Active Directory"
" Domain Controller"
msgstr "Activer le support SSL / TLS vers le contrôleur Active Directory"

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:79
msgid ""
"By default, authentication on Active Directory relies on LDAP SSL "
"(default port 646)."
msgstr ""
"L'authentification Active Directory se fait au travers du protocole LDAP "
"SSL (port 646 par défaut)."

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:82
msgid ""
"SSL/ TLS is not enabled by default on Microsoft Active Directory until a "
"SSL certificate has been configured for the Domain Controller."
msgstr ""
"Microsoft Active Directory n'active pas le support SSL tant qu'un "
"certificat n'a pas été généré et mis en place pour le contrôleur Active "
"Directory."

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:87
msgid ""
"The WAPT Server uses the Certificate Authority *bundles* from the "
"operating system (CentOS) for validating the SSL/ TLS connection to "
"Active Directory."
msgstr ""
"Les *bundles* de certificats utilisés par le serveur WAPT pour valider le"
" certificat du contrôleur Active Directory sont ceux utilisés par défaut "
"par la distribution CentOS."

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:90
msgid ""
"If the Active Directory certificate is self-signed or has been signed by "
"an internal CA, you'll need to add these certificates to the certificate "
"store of CentOS."
msgstr ""
"Si le certificat du contrôleur Active Directory est auto-signé, il faudra"
" faire le nécessaire afin de rajouter au bundle local de CA de CentOS."

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:94
msgid ""
"Add a :term:`Certificate Authority` in the :file:`/etc/pki/ca-"
"trust/source/anchors/` and update the CA store."
msgstr ""
"Ajouter l':term:`Autorité de Certification` dans le dossier "
":file:`/etc/pki/ca-trust/source/anchors/` et mettre à jour les CA."

#: ../../source/waptserver-install/security/security-configuration-auth-ad.rst:102
msgid ""
"Once you have setup LDAP SSL/ TLS on your Active Directory (please refer "
"to Microsoft documentation for that), then you can enable support for "
"SSL/ TLS security for AD in :file:`/opt/wapt/conf/waptserver.ini`:"
msgstr ""
"une fois le certificat mis en place et le support de LDAP SSL sur le "
"contrôleur Active Directory effectué (étape non-documentée), basculer le "
"support SSL / TLS à True dans le fichier "
":file:`/opt/wapt/conf/waptserver.ini` :"

